<p>Wednesday 30 May</p>
<p>Lovely Day.<br/>Tomorrow our party is due for a trip to Amiens.  <br/>4 German Prisoners today escaped from the Prisoners Compound in Bapaume.<br/>The A.D.M.S. inspected our camp today &amp; was so impressed by the gardens we have made all round the tents and throughout the grounds that tomorrow he intends bring General Tivey along.<br/>Met Bill Cannon today.</p>
